// NVN — Nintendo's graphics API entry point. Resolved from nnSdk via
// the @sdk module tag (defined in config/VersionList.sym). The previous
// attempt put this under @smo:100 which mis-resolved to a stub in
// RedStar.nss instead of nnSdk's actual nvnBootstrapLoader, silently
// breaking the Nvn addon's bootstrap trampoline. See Kgamer77/
// SMOO-Plus-Hakkun for the proven-working module layout.

@sdk

nvnBootstrapLoader
